        <td colspan="2" style="padding-bottom: 6pt"><font style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 10pt">Based on individual performance and record financial results in 2021, including advancing the Firm&#8217;s transformational growth, total
            CEO compensation was set at $35 million</font></td>
        <td style="padding-bottom: 6pt; border-right: #7F7F7F 1pt solid"><font style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 10pt">&#160;</font></td>

            Ratio, and Wealth Management pre-tax margin (excluding integration expenses) met or exceeded their two-year objectives</font></td>

      <tr style="vertical-align: top">
        <td style="padding-top: 6pt; padding-bottom: 10pt"><font style="font-size: 22pt"><b>Compensation Program Objectives and Features</b></font></td>
      </tr>

  </table>
  <p style="font: 14pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #187ABA">Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Stanley</font> has a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">pay for performance philosophy for its Named Executive Officers
      (NEOs), and is committed to responsible compensation programs with the following key objectives, all of which support the Firm's culture and values and shareholders' interests</font></p>
  <p style="font: 14pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #187ABA"><font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt"> <br>
    </font></p>
  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #187ABB"><b> </b></p>
  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0">&#160;</p>
  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&#160;<img src="ny20000909x3_img017.jpg" alt=""></p>
  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"></p>
  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0">&#160;</p>

  <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0"><font style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 8pt; color: #93969C">10</font><font style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif">&#160;</font></p>

  <p style="font: 22pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"></p>
  <p style="font: 22pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><br>
    <b>Framework <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">for</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Determining</font> CEO <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Compensation</font></b></p>
  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: rgb(24,122,186)">&#160;</p>
  <p style="font: 14pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #187ABA">Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Stanley</font> has a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">robust</font> process <font style="letter-spacing: 0.75pt">that</font>
    <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">supports</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">reinforces</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt">the</font> pay <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">for</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">performance








      philosophy</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.75pt">that</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">incorporates</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">following</font> key <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">steps:</font></p>
  <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt"><img src="ny20000909x3_img018.jpg" alt="">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><b> <br>
      </b></font></p>
  <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><font style="font-size: 12pt"><b>MS CEO <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Target </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Compensation</font> Range</b></font><b> <font style="vertical-align: super; font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: -0.5pt">(1)</font></b></p>
  <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0">&#160;</p>
  <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><img src="ny20000909x3_img019.jpg" alt=""></p>
  <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0">&#160;</p>
  <p style="font: 8pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #93959B">The End <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Notes</font> are an <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">integral part</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">this</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">presentation.</font> See <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">slides</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.3pt">21-23</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">for</font>
    <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">information</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">related</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">content</font>
    <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">presented</font> on <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">this</font> page.</p>

  <p style="font: 22pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt"><b>Annual</b></font><b> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Performance </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Priorities</font></b></p>
  <p style="font: 14pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #187ABA">&#160;</p>
  <p style="font: 14pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #187ABA">Each year, <font style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt">the</font> CMDS <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Committee</font> and Board <font style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt">set</font>
    <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">performance</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">priorities</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">with</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">management.</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Performance</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">against</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">these</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">quantitative</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">qualitative</font>
    measures <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">inform</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">executive compensation</font> decisions</p>
  <p style="font: 12pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">&#160;</font></p>

  <p style="font: 22pt/107% Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><b>CEO <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Compensation</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Determination</font></b></p>
  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: rgb(24,122,186)">&#160;</p>
  <p style="font: 14pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #187ABA"><font style="letter-spacing: 0.75pt">At</font> year end, <font style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt">the</font> CMDS <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Committee</font>
    assessed CEO and Firm <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">performance,</font> discussed <font style="letter-spacing: 0.75pt">that</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">assessment</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">with</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt">the</font> Board, and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">established</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.65pt">2021</font> CEO <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">compensation</font></p>
  <p style="text-align: center; font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(24,122,186)">&#160;<img src="ny20000909x3_img021.jpg" alt=""></p>

          <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; color: #187ABA"><b>ROBUST BOARD OVERSIGHT</b></p>
          <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; color: #187ABA"><b>&#160;</b></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt">&#160;&#160;&#160;</font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt">Firm&#8217;s <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">strategy,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">including</font> an <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">annual</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">offsite</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">with</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">management</font></font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt"><br>
            </font></p>
          <p style="margin: -14pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Annual</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt">business <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">plans</font></font></p>

            </font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Enterprise</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt">Risk <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Management</font> (ERM) <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">framework</font></font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: -0.15pt"><br>
            </font></p>

            </font><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.05pt">including</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">diversity</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt">and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">inclusion</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">climate</font> change <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">matters</font></font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt"><br>

          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Culture,</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">values</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt">and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">conduct</font></font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font><font style="font-size: 10pt"><br>
            </font></p>

        </td>
        <td style="border-top: Black 1pt solid; padding: 2pt; width: 20%; border-right: #A9B1B0 1pt solid; border-bottom: #A9B1B0 1pt solid">
          <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; color: #187ABA"><b>ANNUAL BOARD<br>
              EVALUATION</b></p>
          <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; color: #187ABA">&#160;</p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font><font style="font-size: 10pt"><br>
            </font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt">One-on-one <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">interviews</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">for</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">Board,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Independent</font> Lead <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Director</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">committee</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">evaluations</font> include:</font></p>
          <p style="margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8211;</font><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt"></font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.35in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Duties</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt">and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">responsibilities, including individual</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">director</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">performance</font></font></p>
          <p style="margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8211;</font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.35in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt">Board and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">committee</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">structure,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">including</font> board and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">ethnic</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">diversity</font></font></p>
          <p style="margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8211;</font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.35in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Culture,</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt">process and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">execution</font></font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt"></font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Policies</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt">and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">practices </font>are revised as <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">appropriate</font></font></p>
        </td>
        <td style="border-top: Black 1pt solid; padding: 2pt; width: 20%; border-right: #A9B1B0 1pt solid; border-bottom: #A9B1B0 1pt solid">
          <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-top: 3pt; margin-bottom: 3pt; text-align: left; color: #187ABA"><b>SHAREHOLDER RIGHTS<br>
              AND ACCOUNTABILITY</b></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt"><br>
            </font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Adopted</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt">proxy access</font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.05pt"><br>
            </font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.05pt">Shareholders</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt">who own <font style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt">at</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">least</font> 25% <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">of</font> common <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">stock</font>
              may <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">call</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">special</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">meeting</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">shareholders</font></font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.4pt"><br>
            </font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.4pt">All</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">directors</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.25pt">elected</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt">annually</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt">by
              <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">majority</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">vote</font></font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font><font style="font-size: 10pt"><br>
            </font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt">No &#8220;poison <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">pill&#8221;</font> in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">effect</font></font></p>
        </td>
        <td style="border-top: Black 1pt solid; padding: 2pt; width: 20%; border-right: #A9B1B0 1pt solid; border-bottom: #A9B1B0 1pt solid">
          <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; color: #187ABA"><b>COMMITTED TO<br>
              SUSTAINABILITY</b></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.2pt">&#160;&#160;</font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Sustainability</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Report</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">informed</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt">by SASB Guidance</font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.25pt">&#160;&#160;</font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Climate</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt">Change <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">report</font> in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">line</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">with</font> TCFD <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">recommendations</font></font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">&#160;&#160;</font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Pledged</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.5pt">to</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt">reach <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">net-zero financed</font> emissions by 2050</font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt">&#160;&#160;</font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Interim</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt">2030 <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">financed</font> emissions <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">targets</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">for</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">the</font>
              <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">most</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">emissions-intensive</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">sectors within</font> our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">corporate lending</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">portfolio</font></font></p>
        </td>
        <td style="border-top: Black 1pt solid; padding: 2pt; width: 20%; border-bottom: #A9B1B0 1pt solid">
          <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; color: #187ABA"><b>VALUE AND RESPOND TO<br>

          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8226;</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt">&#160;&#160;</font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.2in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Investor</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.2pt">input</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt">in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">recent</font> years has <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">led</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">to:</font></font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.35in; text-indent: -0.15in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8211;</font></p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.35in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt"></font> <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.05pt">Enhanced</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt">proxy <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">disclosure</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">alignment




              </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">compensation</font> and performance, and ESG <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">matters</font></font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.35in; text-indent: -0.15in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8211;</font> </p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.35in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.05pt">Inclusion</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.35pt">of</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt">a Board <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">matrix</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">that</font> shows gender and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">race/ethnicity</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">for</font> each <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">director</font> nominee</font></p>
          <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 3pt 0pt 3pt 0.35in; text-indent: -0.15in"><font style="font-size: 10.5pt">&#8211;</font> </p>
          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.35in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.05pt">Our</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Diversity</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt">and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">Inclusion</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Report</font></font></p>

          <p style="margin: -15pt 0pt 3pt 0.35in; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 'sans-serif'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal;"><font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.05pt">Amendments</font>
            <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.5pt">to</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: 0.3pt">the</font> <font style="font-size: 10pt">Board&#8217;s &#8220;overboarding&#8221; <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">policy</font></font></p>

  <p style="font: 22pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><b>Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">Stanley</font> Has a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">Clear</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">Climate</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Transition </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">Path</font></b></p>
  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: rgb(24,122,186)">&#160;</p>
  <p style="font: 14pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #187ABA">Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">Stanley&#8217;s</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">public</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">commitments</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.75pt">to</font> a low carbon economy are <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">supported</font> by <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">robust</font> governance and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">transparent</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">disclosures</font></p>
  <p style="font: 12pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0">&#160;</p>

  <p style="font: 22pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0pt 10pt"><b>Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">Stanley&#8217;s </font>Board <font style="letter-spacing: 0.9pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Directors</font>
      Recommends <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Shareholders </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">Vote</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Against</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Proposal </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Requesting Policy</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 1.2pt">to</font> Cease <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Financing </font>New <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">Fossil</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.85pt">Fuel</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Development</font></b></p>
  <div style="border: rgb(127,127,127) 1pt solid">
    <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"></p>
    <table style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">

        <tr style="vertical-align: top">
          <td style="width: 0"></td>
          <td style="border-left: rgb(127,127,127) 1pt solid; width: 0.2in"><font style="font-size: 12.5pt">&#8226;</font></td>
          <td><font style="font-size: 12pt">Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Stanley</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">supports</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">transition</font>
              <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">low-carbon</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">economy.</font> We have <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">already</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">committed</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">climate transition</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">path</font> and have announced <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">multiple</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">commitments</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">help</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">facilitate</font>
              <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">this</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">transition.</font></font></td>
        </tr>

    </table>
    <table style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">

        <tr style="vertical-align: top">
          <td style="padding-top: 2pt; width: 0.2in; padding-bottom: 2pt"></td>
          <td style="padding-top: 2pt; width: 0.25in; padding-bottom: 2pt"><font style="font-size: 12.5pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">&#8722;</font></td>
          <td style="padding-top: 2pt; padding-bottom: 2pt"><font style="font-size: 12pt">In <font style="letter-spacing: -0.15pt">2020, </font>we were <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the first</font> major <font style="letter-spacing: -0.4pt">U.S.</font>
              <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">headquartered</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">global</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">financial</font> services <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">firm</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">commit</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> achieve <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Net-Zero</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">financed</font>
              emissions by <font style="letter-spacing: -0.15pt">2050.</font> This</font> <font style="font-size: 12.5pt">commitment</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt">was reviewed by our Board and is <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">consistent</font>
              <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">with</font> our membership in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">United</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">Nations-convened</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Net-Zero</font> Banking <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Alliance.</font></font></td>
        </tr>

    </table>
    <table style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">

          <td style="padding-top: 2pt; padding-bottom: 2pt"><font style="font-size: 12pt">In <font style="letter-spacing: -0.65pt">2021,</font> we <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">publicly</font> announced our 2030 <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">interim</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">financed</font> emissions <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">targets</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">for</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">auto</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">manufacturing,</font> energy and <font style="letter-spacing: -0.15pt">power, </font>which we <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">identified</font> as <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">most</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">emissions-intensive</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">sectors</font> in our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">corporate</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">lending</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">portfolio.</font> Our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">reduction</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">targets,</font> which cover <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">client</font> Scope <font style="letter-spacing: -1.65pt">1,</font> Scope 2 and Scope 3 emissions and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt">all</font> greenhouse <font style="letter-spacing: -0.15pt">gases, </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">inclusive</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">corporate</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">lending</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">portfolio,</font> are <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">consistent</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">with,</font> and sourced</font> <font style="font-size: 12.5pt">from</font><font style="font-size: 12pt">, <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> emissions <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">pathways</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">for these</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">sectors</font> as <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">modeled</font> in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">International</font> Energy Agency (&#8220;IEA&#8221;) <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Net-Zero</font> Emissions
              by 2050 Scenario <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">that</font> is <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">requested</font> by <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> proposal.</font></td>

              source <font style="letter-spacing: -0.85pt">100</font></font> <font style="font-size: 12.5pt">percent</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt">our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">global</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">operational</font> needs <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">from</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">renewable</font> energy and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">offset</font>
              any remaining <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">emissions.</font></font></td>

              <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">also</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">conduct</font> enhanced due <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">diligence</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">for</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">transactions.</font></font></td>

          <td style="padding-top: 3pt; padding-bottom: 3pt"><font style="font-size: 12pt">Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Stanley</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">believes</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">it</font> is <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">well</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">positioned</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">help</font> companies make progress in addressing <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">transition</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">low-carbon</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">economy</font>
              by providing our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">knowledge</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">support</font> our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">clients</font> on <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">their</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">transition</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">journey.</font></font></td>
        </tr>

          <td style="padding-top: 3pt; width: 0.2in; padding-bottom: 3pt"></td>
          <td style="padding-top: 3pt; width: 0.2in; padding-bottom: 3pt"><font style="font-size: 12.5pt">&#8722;</font></td>
          <td style="padding-top: 3pt; padding-bottom: 3pt"><font style="font-size: 12pt">Morgan</font> <font style="font-size: 12.5pt">Stanley&#8217;s</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt">approach <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> being an <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">advocate</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">for</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">thoughtfully</font> managing <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">climate</font> risk and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">contributing</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">decarbonization,</font> which we have <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">developed</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">within</font> our own <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">organization,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">facilitates</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">path</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">for other</font> companies <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">meet</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">their









                climate</font> risk <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">management</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">objectives.</font></font></td>
        </tr>

    </table>
    <table style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">

        <tr style="vertical-align: top">
          <td style="padding-top: 3pt; width: 0; padding-bottom: 3pt"></td>
          <td style="padding-top: 3pt; width: 0.2in; padding-bottom: 3pt"><font style="font-size: 12.5pt">&#8226;</font></td>
          <td style="padding-top: 3pt; padding-bottom: 3pt"><font style="font-size: 12pt">The <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">transition</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">to</font> a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">low-carbon</font>
              economy is <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">complex</font> and requires <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">intentional</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">balancing</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of</font> risks and
              <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">opportunities.</font> The <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">proposal</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">unnecessarily</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">restricts</font> Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Stanley&#8217;s</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">ability</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">conduct</font> our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">operations</font>
              by <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">inherently</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">limiting</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">lending</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">underwriting</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">activities</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">that</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">&#8220;contribute</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">to&#8221;</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">fossil</font>
              <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">fuel</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">expansion,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">potentially</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">affecting</font> a broad array <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">clients.</font> The <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">proposal</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">could</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">lead</font>
              <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">far-reaching</font> consequences <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">that</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">could</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">affect</font> our business <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">decisions,</font> require <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">meaningful</font> resources <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">implement,</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">impact</font> our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">relationships</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">with</font> our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">clients</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">other</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">stakeholder</font><font style="letter-spacing: -1.05pt">s</font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">.</font></font></td>
        </tr>

    </table>
    <table style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">

        <tr style="vertical-align: top">
          <td style="padding-top: 3pt; width: 0.2in; padding-bottom: 3pt"></td>
          <td style="padding-top: 3pt; width: 0.2in; padding-bottom: 3pt"><font style="font-size: 12.5pt">&#8722;</font></td>
          <td style="padding-top: 3pt; padding-bottom: 3pt"><font style="font-size: 12pt">Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Stanley</font> recognizes <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">societal</font>
              risks posed by <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">climate</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">change.</font> As discussed <font style="letter-spacing: -0.15pt">above,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">despite</font>
              Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Stanley&#8217;s</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">existing</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">public</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">commitments</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">transition</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">low-carbon</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">economy,</font>
              <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">proposal</font> seeks <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> impose <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">specific</font> measures and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">dictate</font> a prescribed <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">method</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> achieve such <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">policy</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">that</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">limits</font> Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Stanley&#8217;s</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">discretion.</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Implementation</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">proposal</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">could</font> require Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Stanley</font>
              <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">take</font> measures <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> avoid new financings, and cease <font style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt">all</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">forms</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of</font> ongoing financings, <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">clients</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">that</font> are <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">involved</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.25pt">in,</font> or <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">otherwise</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">indirectly</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">contribute</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">to,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">fossil</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">fuel</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">development.</font></font></td>
        </tr>

              approach <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">complicated objective</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of</font> reducing carbon
              emissions does <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">not</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">leave</font> room <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">for</font> Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Stanley</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">management</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> weigh <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">complex</font> variables, and manage <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">associated</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.15pt">risks, </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">that</font> are needed in deciding <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">whether</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">enter</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">into</font> new businesses or manage our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">existing</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">obligations.</font></font></td>

  <p style="font: 8pt/107% Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #868686"><font style="letter-spacing: -0.75pt">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="font: 22pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><b>Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">Stanley&#8217;s </font>Board <font style="letter-spacing: 0.9pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Directors</font> Recommends <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Shareholders </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">Vote</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Against</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Proposal </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Requesting




        Policy</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 1.2pt">to</font> Cease <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Financing </font>New <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">Fossil</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.85pt">Fuel</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Development</font></b></p>
  <div style="border: rgb(127,127,127) 1pt solid">
    <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0 0pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in">&#160;</p>
    <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0 0pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 12.5pt">&#8226;</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt">&#160;&#160;From a risk <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">perspective,</font> we have
        been <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">intensely</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">focused</font> on <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">integrating</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">climate</font> risk <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">considerations</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">into</font> our risk <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">management</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">processes.</font> We <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">believe</font> our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Net-Zero</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">commitment</font> and our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">interim</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">targets</font> discussed above <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">will</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">help</font> reduce our exposure <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">transition</font> risk <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">from</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">most</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">emissions-intensive</font>
        companies over <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">time.</font></font></p>
    <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0 0pt 0.4in; text-indent: -0.2in">&#160;</p>
    <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0 0pt 0.4in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 12.5pt">&#8722;</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt">&#160;We <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">expect</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> reduce our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">transition</font> risk <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">through</font> sound <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">client</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">engagement</font> and risk <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">management</font> processes <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">that</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">support</font> our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">clients&#8217; transition</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">to</font> more <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">sustainable,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">lower-carbon</font> business <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">models</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">that</font> may be <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">less</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">vulnerable</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font>
        changes in policy, <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">technology</font> and consumer <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">sentiments.</font></font></p>
    <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0 0pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in">&#160;</p>
    <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0 0pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 12.5pt">&#8226;</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt">&#160;&#160;While</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt">we have <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">utilized</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">most</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">relevant</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">part</font>
        <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of</font> IEA Program Finance <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Initiative</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> guide our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">financed</font> emissions <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">pathway,</font> we did <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">not</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">commit</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">completely</font>
        <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">instituting</font> every <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">aspect</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">initiative</font> as <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">it</font> is <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">critical</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">that</font> we <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">adapt</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font>
        <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">initiative</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">what</font> is <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">best</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">for</font>
        Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Stanley</font> and our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">stakeholders.</font></font></p>
    <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0 0pt 0.4in; text-indent: -0.2in">&#160;</p>
    <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0 0pt 0.4in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 12.5pt">&#8722;</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 0.15pt">&#160;While</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 0.3pt">this</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">framework</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 0.3pt">calls</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 0.25pt">for</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt">an <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">immediate</font> end <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">fossil</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">fuel</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">expansion,</font> we <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">believe</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">that</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">there</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">must</font>
        be a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">balancing</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">the potential</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">impacts</font> on Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Stanley,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> economy and on <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">society.</font></font></p>
    <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0 0pt 0.4in; text-indent: -0.2in">&#160;</p>
    <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0 0pt 0.4in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 12.5pt">&#8722;</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 0.6pt">&#160;At</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 0.3pt">this</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">time,</font> <font style="font-size: 12pt">we <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">believe</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">immediately</font> removing <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">support</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">from</font> key <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">sectors</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">like</font> energy (or even providing in a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">policy</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">for</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">removal</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">support</font>
        by a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">future</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">date)</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">would</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">also</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">likely</font>
        undermine a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">smooth</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">climate transition</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">role</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.6pt">that</font> Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">Stanley</font> can play.</font></p>
    <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0 0pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in">&#160;</p>
    <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0 0pt 0.2in; text-indent: -0.2in"><font style="font-size: 12.5pt">&#8226; </font>&#160;&#160;<font style="font-size: 12pt"><b>For <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">foregoing </font>reasons, <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">the</font> Board <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">believes</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">the </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">policy requested</font> by <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">proposal </font>is unnecessary in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">light</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt">of</font>
          our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Net-Zero </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">commitment,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">interim</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">financed </font>emissions <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">targets</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">other</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">public </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">commitments; robust</font> risk <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">management</font> programs and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">policies;</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">ability</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.65pt">to </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">assist</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">clients</font> in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">their transition</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.65pt">to</font> a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">low-carbon</font> economy.</b></font></p>
  </div>

  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><b>The <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">following notes</font> are an <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">integral</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">part</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">of </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">the</font> Firm&#8217;s <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">financial</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">operating </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">performance</font>
      described in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">this</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">presentation:</font></b></p>
  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #187ABA"><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #187ABA"><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt"><b>General</b></font></p>
  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0">&#160;</p>
  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><font style="font-size: 9pt">A <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">detailed </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">analysis</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">of the</font>
      Firm&#8217;s <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">financial </font>and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">operational</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">performance</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">for </font><font style="letter-spacing: -0.45pt">2021</font> is <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">contained</font> in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">Management&#8217;s </font>Discussion and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">Analysis</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">Financial </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Condition</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Results</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">of </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Operations</font> in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">[Part</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.2pt">II, </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Item</font> 7] <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">of the</font>
      Firm&#8217;s <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Annual </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Report</font> on Form <font style="letter-spacing: -0.45pt">10-K</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">for </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">the</font> year ended December <font style="letter-spacing: -0.8pt">31,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.45pt">2021 </font><font style="letter-spacing: -0.3pt">(&#8216;2021</font> Form <font style="letter-spacing: -0.35pt">10-K&#8217;).</font>
      This <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">presentation</font> may <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">refer</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">to </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">certain</font> non-GAAP <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">financial</font> measures which we <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">believe</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">to</font> be <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">useful </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.2pt">us,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">investors, </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">analysts</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">other</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">stakeholders </font>by providing <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">further</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">transparency about,</font> or an <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">additional</font> means
      <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">of</font> assessing our <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">financial condition</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">operating results.</font> The <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">definition </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">of</font> such non-GAAP <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">financial</font> measures and/or <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">reconciliation</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">of </font>such measures <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">comparable</font> GAAP <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">figures </font>is <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">included</font> in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">either</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">the </font><font style="letter-spacing: -0.45pt">2021</font> Form <font style="letter-spacing: -0.45pt">10-K</font>
      or <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">herein.</font></font></p>

            <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">Sachs, </font><font style="letter-spacing: -1.15pt">JP</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">Morgan, </font>and <font style="letter-spacing: -0.15pt">UBS.</font> Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Stanley&#8217;s </font>ISG <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">wallet</font> share <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">represents </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">total</font> ISG <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">segment </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">net</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.05pt">revenues. </font>Peer <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">wallet</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">includes </font>revenues <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">that</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">represent </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Investment</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">Banking, </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Equity</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Sales </font>&amp; Trading and Fixed Income <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Sales</font> &amp; <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">Trading, </font>where









            <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">applicable. </font>For <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">firms</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">that </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">disclose</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">results </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">between</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">multiple </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">segments,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">assumptions </font>have









            been made based on company disclosures. Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Stanley&#8217;s </font><font style="letter-spacing: -0.45pt">2014</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Wallet </font>Share is <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">calculated</font> as <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">the </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">percentage</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">of </font>Morgan <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Stanley&#8217;s</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">net </font><font style="letter-spacing: -0.05pt">revenues,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">excluding </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">positive</font> DVA <font style="letter-spacing: -0.35pt">($651 </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">million)</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">to </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">Wallet </font>and has been <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">restated</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">to </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">conform</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">with </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">current
              reporting</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">methodology. </font>Peer <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">data for</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.45pt">2014 </font>has been <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">adjusted</font>
            <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">for </font><font style="letter-spacing: -0.15pt">DVA, </font>where <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">it </font>is <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">reported</font> and where <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">applicable.</font></font></td>

  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #187ABA"><b>Page <font style="letter-spacing: -0.85pt">13</font></b></p>
  <p style="font: 9.5pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0"><font style="letter-spacing: -1.3pt">&#160;</font></p>
  <table style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">

      <tr style="vertical-align: top">
        <td style="width: 0.6pt"></td>
        <td style="width: 17.7pt"><font style="font-size: 9.5pt; letter-spacing: -1.3pt">1.</font></td>
        <td><font style="font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Pursuant</font> <font style="font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0.4pt">to</font> <font style="font-size: 9pt">SEC rules, <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">the</font> Summary <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">Compensation</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Table</font> in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">the</font> Firm&#8217;s proxy <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">statement</font> is required <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">include</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">for</font> a <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">particular</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">year,
            </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">only those equity</font> awards <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">granted</font> during <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">year, </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">rather</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">than</font> awards <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">granted</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">after</font> year end <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">that</font> were awarded <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">for</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">performance</font> in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">that</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">year. </font>Our








            <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">annual</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">equity</font> awards <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">relating</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">performance</font> in a year are made <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">shortly</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">after</font> year <font style="letter-spacing: -0.15pt">end.</font> Therefore, <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">the</font> Summary <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">Compensation</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Table</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">that</font> appears in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">the</font> Firm&#8217;s 2022 proxy <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">statement</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">includes</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">not</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">only</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">non-equity</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">compensation</font> awarded <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">for</font> service in <font style="letter-spacing: -0.5pt">2021,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">but</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">also stock</font> awards and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">forward-looking</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">performance</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">vested</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">compensation</font> in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">respect</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">performance</font> in <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">2020, </font>in each case <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">granted</font> in <font style="letter-spacing: -0.5pt">2021.</font></font></td>
      </tr>

  </table>
  <p style="font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0; color: #187ABA">&#160;</p>

            each <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">director&#8217;s professional</font> experience and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">qualifications,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">skills</font> and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">attributes,</font>
            see <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">&#8220;Director</font> Nominees&#8221; <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">of the</font> 2022 Proxy <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Statement.</font></font></td>

  <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0">&#160;</p>
  <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0">The <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">information</font> provided herein may <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">include</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">certain</font>
    non-GAAP <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">financial</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.1pt">measures.</font> The <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">definition</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of</font> such <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">financial</font> measures and/or <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">reconciliation</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">of</font> such measures <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">comparable</font> GAAP <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">figures</font> are <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">included</font>
    in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">the</font> Firm&#8217;s <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Annual</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">Report</font> on Form <font style="letter-spacing: -0.55pt">10-K</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">for</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">the</font> year ended December <font style="letter-spacing: -1pt">31,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.6pt">2021,</font> which is <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">available</font>
    on www.morganstanley.com, or <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">within</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">this</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">presentation.</font> The <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">endnotes</font> on
    pages <font style="letter-spacing: -0.45pt">21-23</font> are an <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">integral</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">part</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">this</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">presentation.</font></p>
  <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0">&#160;</p>
  <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0">This <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">presentation</font> may <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">contain</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">forward-looking</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">statements.</font> You are <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">cautioned</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">not</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">place</font>
    undue <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">reliance</font> on <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">forward-looking</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">statements,</font> which speak <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">only</font> as <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">date</font> on which <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">they</font> are <font style="letter-spacing: -0.15pt">made, </font>which








    <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">reflect</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">management&#8217;s</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">current estimates,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">projections,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">expectations</font> or <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">beliefs</font> and which are <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">subject</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">to</font> risks and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">uncertainties</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">that</font> may cause <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">actual</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">results</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.5pt">to</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">differ</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">materially.</font> For a discussion <font style="letter-spacing: 0.4pt">of</font> risks and <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">uncertainties</font>
    <font style="letter-spacing: 0.55pt">that</font> may <font style="letter-spacing: 0.45pt">affect</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.3pt">future</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">results</font>
    <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">of the</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.15pt">Firm, </font><font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">please</font> see <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">the</font> Firm&#8217;s <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">Annual</font>
    <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">Report</font> on Form <font style="letter-spacing: -0.55pt">10-K</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">for</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">the</font> year ended December <font style="letter-spacing: -1pt">31,</font> <font style="letter-spacing: -0.6pt">2021.</font></p>
  <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0">&#160;</p>
  <p style="font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0pt 0">The <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">statements</font> in <font style="letter-spacing: 0.25pt">this</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">presentation</font> are <font style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt">current only</font> as <font style="letter-spacing: 0.35pt">of</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.2pt">their</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.1pt">respective</font> <font style="letter-spacing: 0.05pt">dates.</font></p>
